{"prompt": "Generate a website for a financial consulting. The website should be cozy and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Redwood Financial Consulting</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8f4f0; /* Light cream background */\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(178, 34, 34, 0.8), rgba(178, 34, 34, 0.8)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580587771525-78b9dba3b914?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80'); /* Redwood red gradient with background image */\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            box-shadow: inset 0 0 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #a32638; /* Darker redwood red */\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-left: 5px solid #a32638; /* Redwood red border */\n            background-color: #fdfaf7; /* Slightly warmer background for service items */\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.2s ease-in-out;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: #a32638; /* Redwood red icon */\n            margin-right: 25px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            background-color: rgba(178, 34, 34, 0.08); /* Subtle redwood red background for icon */\n            border-radius: 50%;\n        }\n        .service-item-text h3 {\n            margin: 0 0 10px 0;\n            color: #a32638; /* Redwood red */\n            font-size: 1.6em;\n        }\n        .service-item-text p {\n            margin: 0;\n            line-height: 1.7;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n        .contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        .contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            background-color: #fefefe;\n            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form input[type=\"text\"]:focus,\n        .contact-form input[type=\"email\"]:focus,\n        .contact-form textarea:focus {\n            border-color: #a32638; /* Redwood red focus border */\n            outline: none;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #a32638; /* Redwood red button */\n            color: white;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #7f1d2d; /* Darker redwood red on hover */\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            background-color: #a32638; /* Redwood red footer */\n            color: #f8f4f0; /* Light cream text */\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        /* Font Awesome for icons */\n        .fas {\n            font-family: \"Font Awesome 5 Free\";\n            font-weight: 900;\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Redwood Financial Consulting</h1>\n        <p>Guiding your financial future with wisdom and clarity.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Services</h2>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n            <div class=\"service-item-text\">\n                <h3>Investment Strategies</h3>\n                <p>Tailored investment plans designed to grow your wealth securely and efficiently, aligning with your personal risk tolerance and financial goals.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-piggy-bank\"></i>\n            <div class=\"service-item-text\">\n                <h3>Retirement Planning</h3>\n                <p>Develop a robust retirement plan to ensure a comfortable and financially secure future, no matter your age or current situation.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-hand-holding-usd\"></i>\n            <div class=\"service-item-text\">\n                <h3>Financial Planning</h3>\n                <p>Comprehensive financial planning services covering budgeting, debt management, savings, and long-term financial health.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt\"></i>\n            <div class=\"service-item-text\">\n                <h3>Risk Management</h3>\n                <p>Assess and mitigate financial risks to protect your assets and secure your financial well-being against unforeseen circumstances.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container contact-form\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <p>Let's discuss how we can help you achieve your financial aspirations.</p>\n        <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n            <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n            <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n            <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n            <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n        </form>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Redwood Financial Consulting. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple animation for service items on scroll\n        const serviceItems = document.querySelectorAll('.service-item');\n        const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n            entries.forEach(entry => {\n                if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n                    entry.target.style.opacity = '1';\n                    entry.target.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';\n                } else {\n                    entry.target.style.opacity = '0';\n                    entry.target.style.transform = 'translateY(20px)';\n                }\n            });\n        }, { threshold: 0.1 });\n\n        serviceItems.forEach(item => {\n            item.style.opacity = '0';\n            item.style.transform = 'translateY(20px)';\n            item.style.transition = 'opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out';\n            observer.observe(item);\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}